OL,3,CThree seriously injured after
OL,4,Ccollision in Nottinghamshire village
OL,6,FThree people have been taken to
OL,7,Fhospital after a serious collision in
OL,8,Fa Nottinghamshire village.
OL,10,FEmergency services were called to
OL,11,FLinby Lane, in Linby, just before 9pm
OL,12,Fon Friday, June 5, after the three
OL,13,Fvictims were hit while walking on a
OL,14,Ffootpath.
OL,16,FA man and a woman aged in their 60s
OL,17,Fsustained serious injuries while an 18-
OL,18,Fyear-old man remains in a critical
OL,19,Fcondition.
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G1/4
