OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F378A1780924280
OL,3,CThree seriously injured after
OL,4,Ccollision in Nottinghamshire village
OL,6,FNottinghamshire Police said all three
OL,7,Fremain in hospital on Saturday, June 6.
OL,9,FPolice say a 23-year-old man was
OL,10,Farrested on suspicion of dangerous
OL,11,Fdriving and driving while unfit
OL,12,Fthrough drink or drugs. He remains in
OL,13,Fpolice custody.
OL,15,FLinby Lane remained closed overnight
OL,16,Fbetween Moor Road and Wighay Road
OL,17,Fwhile emergency services responded to
OL,18,Fthe incident.
OL,20,FThe closure was then lifted at around
OL,21,F8am on Saturday morning.
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G2/4
OL,2,W+.! +,*%/"-'"-$/*%/*%/.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
