CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F378A1780924280
OL,3,CThree seriously injured after
OL,4,Ccollision in Nottinghamshire village
OL,6,FDetective Sergeant Charlotte Henson,
OL,7,Fof Nottinghamshire Police's Serious
OL,8,FCollision Investigation Unit, said:
OL,9,F"This collision occurred on a busy
OL,10,Fstretch of road and we believe there
OL,11,Fwill be a number of witnesses who may
OL,12,Fhave seen the vehicle involved, a blue
OL,13,FBMW, in the moments before the
OL,14,Fincident.
OL,16,F"If you can help, and have not yet
OL,17,Fspoken to an officer, please get in
OL,18,Ftouch without delay.
OL,26,@xD@AOU
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G3/4
